                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.51/439.</note>
                        <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Port au Prince</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-11-30">
                                    <hi rend="italic">November 30, 1915</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>French Government has officially recognized Dartiguenave Government.
                            British Chargé d’Affaires has instructions to recognize Dartiguenave
                            Government.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Caperton</hi>.</signed>
                        </closer>
